originalText.text: Love, love, love Alexa’s work! Hands down the best aesthetic nurse practitioner in NYC! She is truly remarkable, so knowledgeable and just a fun person to be around. She treats you like her family and I always feel at ease in her hands. Every time I walk out of her office I feel and look younger and more confident. Her office is gorgeous, and the staff is so attentive and kind.I can't wait for my next visit for botox & filler!

originalText.text: Alexa is the goddess of injectables! She was my first ever experience with Botox and now I will not ever go to anyone else. From the time she walked into the room, she extremely knowledgeable and professional. She clearly articulated every step of the process including sensations to expect. She was spot on every time! My results were beyond my expectations. Thanks to her I look and  feel youthful and confident. I cannot recommend her enough!

originalText.text: I've known Alexa for a large portion of her career from bedside in the ICU to her aesthetic practice, and everywhere in between. She's committed to excellence and provides safe, appropriate care; you'll feel like family with her. Her attention to detail and vast knowledge is incredible. You can trust that you will have a great experience, and she will tailor her treatments to your specific needs.

originalText.text: I’m not usually a person who gets Botox or other aesthetic treatments, but I wanted to look well rested for my wedding. Alexa explained the process of fillers and how they would enhance my natural beauty. She was so knowledgeable about the process, the science behind the placement of the fillers, and the recovery that it made me feel at ease. As a result, I had a natural looking enhancement that did not look fake, and I had some excellent wedding photos! I wouldn’t trust anyone else with my face!

originalText.text: Alexa has been my injector for years. I visited her initially when I had some bad lip fillers done, and she laid out a concise plan that would help me achieve the beauty goals I desired. She is the most professional and honest person that I’ve come to know in the beauty industry, and with her background as a nurse practitioner, I know I can always trust my face in her hands.
